{
  "stem": "25809.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as the water heats up and heats up, all of a sudden, bit by bit, the frog realizes the water has gotten so hot that he can't jump out of the pot anymore.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this is the approach that the Germans did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They just built up the heat bit by bit by bit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "First, everybody had to report.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then, it became necessary for everybody to wear a Jewish star.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody who was Jewish had to report.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had to-- needed an Ausweis, a passport or identification papers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the identification papers would show that you were a Jew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because it had a J stamped on it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then later on, you, you had to wear the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then later on, all of a sudden--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, very distinctly, very distinctly-- because I remember in later years, and I'm talking living in Hawaii when I was in my-- maybe, like 10 years ago, I was the technical assistant to the play of And one of the girls-- and I'm moving way ahead now to give you an explanation on that yellow star-- one of the girls that was doing the detailing for the dress, for the dressing and how to dress the people, walked up to me.",
      "word_count": 82
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, I copied this from an, from an information book.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she laid in front of me the yellow star I had worn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was like somebody, all of a sudden, hit me with a two-by-four in the face.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I literally went-- yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I, I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I wanted to be professional about this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I wanted to keep my emotion out of this whole thing and caught myself.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
